# Sajtmaskin - Project Overview

AI-powered website builder where users describe a website in natural language
and get a working site generated, previewed, and deployed.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript 5.9
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui (Radix primitives)
- **AI/Generation**: v0 Platform API (v0-sdk), AI SDK 6 (@ai-sdk/openai, @ai-sdk/vercel)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (Supabase) via Drizzle ORM
- **Cache**: Redis (Upstash/ioredis)
- **State**: Zustand (auth), React hooks (builder state)
- **Payments**: Stripe
- **Deploy target**: Vercel (user sites deployed via Vercel API)
- **Storage**: Vercel Blob (AI-generated images)

## Architecture

```
User prompt -> Builder UI -> v0 Platform API -> Generated code -> Preview -> Deploy to Vercel
```

### Key directories

| Directory | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `src/app/builder/` | Main builder page (prompt -> generate -> preview -> deploy) |
| `src/app/admin/` | Admin dashboard |
| `src/app/api/v0/` | v0 Platform API proxy routes (chat, stream, projects) |
| `src/app/api/auth/` | Authentication (email, Google, GitHub OAuth) |
| `src/app/api/ai/` | AI Gateway routes (prompt assist, brief, spec) |
| `src/components/builder/` | Builder UI components (ChatInterface, MessageList, PreviewPanel) |![1772500015428](image/project-overview/1772500015428.png)
| `src/components/ai-elements/` | AI Elements components (prompt input, reasoning, code blocks) |
| `src/components/ui/` | shadcn/ui base components |
| `src/lib/v0/` | v0 SDK wrapper, streaming, file parsing |
| `src/lib/builder/` | Builder business logic (prompt assist, orchestration, types) |
| `src/lib/hooks/` | React hooks (useV0ChatMessaging, useChat, useVersions) |
| `src/lib/db/` | Drizzle schema + service layer |
| `src/lib/auth/` | Auth logic + Zustand store + edge-auth.ts for middleware |
| `src/lib/brave-search.ts` | Brave Web Search API wrapper |
| `src/proxy.ts` | Centralized auth redirects, CORS, security headers (Node.js runtime) |
| `LLM/` | AI/prompt strategy notes |

### Core flow (builder)

1. User enters prompt in `ChatInterface.tsx`
2. Prompt optionally enhanced via `/api/ai/chat` (prompt assist)
3. Sent to `/api/v0/chats/stream` or `/api/v0/chats/[chatId]/stream`
4. v0 Platform API generates code, streamed back via SSE
5. Preview rendered in `PreviewPanel.tsx`
6. User can refine, deploy, or start new

### Database tables (Drizzle)

projects, chats, versions, deployments, users, transactions, user_integrations

### Config

All env vars accessed through `src/lib/config.ts` (SECRETS, FEATURES, PATHS, URLS).
Feature flags auto-detect available services.

## Conventions

- Language: Swedish for user-facing copy, English for code/comments/logs
- Path alias: `@/*` maps to `src/*`
- Barrel exports: `index.ts` in component directories
- API routes handle auth via session cookies (see `src/proxy.ts`)
